&lt;DIV&gt;What question would you like to ask a developer about the necromancer class?&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Every week (in the current form, but subject to change) each correspondent will be asking one question of the developers. The main questions I've been asking are basically about top ten issues and hotbutton issues. I will leave this thread stickied for a while, and I'll heavilly moderate it for anything that isn't a question or helpful. We can make discussion threads on individual issues, however this thread will merely serve as a reference for the correspondent in constructing the weekly question.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Remember there won't be polling or anything, but if I like your question, and especially if it isn't a "gimmee", SOE envy, or class envy orientated, it stands a decent chance of getting asked by me. Responses by the devs aren't guarenteed either, but I will continue to do my best in getting those answers.&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
